## Scope of this license

This MIT License covers the **free and open-source parts** of the Hono UI
project:

- The `@hono-ui/cli` package on npm
- The `@hono-ui/enhance` package on npm
- All source files under `registry/ui/` (free UI primitives)
- All source files under `registry/lib/` (shared library helpers)
- All source files under `registry/blocks/free/` (free marketing and utility
  blocks)
- The documentation site source in `docs/`

The **paid Pro blocks** under `registry/blocks/pro/` are covered by a separate
commercial license. See `LICENSE-PRO.md` for terms that apply to Pro blocks,
or visit https://honoui.com/license for the web version.
